<td valign="top" style="padding-right:30px; padding-left:20px;">
<div id="Idea_3211"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3211-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3211">Pork early warning system&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/4612-4049">azaleahs</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">5 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">A map of the US showing the location of every government project, both Federal and state. By moving the mouse arrow over the flag at each site it would show the expenditure, who authorized it etc. and by clicking on the arrow provide more information and links to media stories etc.</div>
